(1913, 610, '_elementor_data', '[{"id":"2dde3ddd","elType":"section","settings":{"structure":"20"},"elements":[{"id":"7451fc65","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":50,"_inline_size":62.983},"elements":[{"id":"7c4aa6b5","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<h3><strong><span style=\\"color: #ff0000;\\">ADULT IELTS 4.0<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/h3><p style=\\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: #313439; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif;\\">\\u0110\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 gi\\u00e1o vi\\u00ean gi\\u00e0u kinh nghi\\u1ec7m t\\u1ea1i Ocean Edu \\u0111\\u00e3 d\\u00e0nh nhi\\u1ec1u th\\u1eddi gian bi\\u00ean so\\u1ea1n ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh luy\\u1ec7n thi ADULT IELTS 4.0, gi\\u00fap c\\u00e1c h\\u1ecdc vi\\u00ean d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng l\\u00e0m quen v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ec1 thi IELTS, c\\u00e1c b\\u00e0i thi th\\u1eed IELTS.<\\/p><h4 style=\\"margin-top: 0px;\\">L\\u1ee3i \\u00edch kh\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc<\\/h4><p style=\\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: #313439; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif;\\">Kh\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc trang b\\u1ecb cho c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n h\\u1ecdc vi\\u00ean ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c Anh ng\\u1eef s\\u00e2u r\\u1ed9ng, ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed3ng b\\u1ed9 c\\u00e1c k\\u1ef9 n\\u0103ng v\\u1ec1 c\\u1ea3 t\\u1eeb v\\u1ef1ng, ng\\u1eef ph\\u00e1p, ph\\u00e1t \\u00e2m chu\\u1ea9n \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 th\\u00e0nh th\\u1ea1o s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng Ti\\u1ebfng Anh:<\\/p><ul style=\\"color: #313439; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif;\\"><li>Luy\\u1ec7n t\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng ph\\u00e1t \\u00e2m kh\\u00f3 v\\u00e0 ph\\u1ee9c t\\u1ea1p h\\u01a1n nh\\u01b0 n\\u1ed1i \\u00e2m, ng\\u1eef \\u0111i\\u1ec7u, n\\u00f3i c\\u00e2u d\\u00e0i v\\u00e0 \\u0111o\\u1ea1n v\\u0103n;<\\/li><li>Luy\\u1ec7n ph\\u1ea3n x\\u1ea1 giao ti\\u1ebfp, chu\\u1ea9n ng\\u1eef ph\\u00e1p v\\u00e0 t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean, t\\u1ea1o h\\u1ed9i tho\\u1ea1i trong c\\u00e1c t\\u00ecnh hu\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u1eddi s\\u1ed1ng khi g\\u1eb7p ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi n\\u01b